author: WCAX News
title: Lyme disease remains a threat
text:
BURLINGTON, Vt. - Autumn is officially here, but the danger of Lyme disease still lingers. Ticks are a threat well into October.
Bradley Thompkins, an epidemiologist with the Vermont Department of Health, discusses the latest on Lyme.
Watch the video for more information.
